                             'ArcheoBot' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'ArcheoBot' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} in which the time is 1 million
years in the future, the human race has left Earth a long time ago
and colonized many new worlds. However, even though there are some
records from Earth, humans have forgotten the exact location of the
planet where they originated. So, research spaceships were sent in
all known and unknown places of the universe, in order to find the
goode ole' planet Earth...

  Your job, as you may have guessed, is to find evidence of Earth's
past; you control 'ArcheoBots', robots that are specially built for
archeological purposes, to explore various areas to collect
artifacts, these are: garbage, automobiles and human skeletons...

  Have fun!

